Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Just Proportioning of
    Ritual
By: Eckhart
---
If I intend to cross the sea and want a ship, that is part and parcel
of the wishing to be over and having gotten to the other side I do not
want the ship.
